OL,6,FWords by Georgia Ziebart, ITV News
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FHouseholds across the UK are expected
OL,10,Fto benefit from significantly higher
OL,11,Fpay outs to compensate for water
OL,12,Fcompany failures.
OL,14,FThe government announced the changes,
OL,15,Fwhich will see new and increased
OL,16,Fcompensation become compulsory for
OL,17,Fcustomers, following a public
OL,18,Fconsultation.
