OL,3,CWater firm pay outs: Who is eligible
OL,4,Cand how much compensation will be paid?
OL,6,FBut who will be eligible for the
OL,7,Fpayments, and how much will the
OL,8,Fcompensation be?
OL,10,FITV News explains what you need to
OL,11,Fknow.
OL,13,FWhy are the changes being made?
OL,15,FThe government say the reforms
OL,16,Funderscore their commitments to hold
OL,17,Fwater companies to account for poor
OL,18,Fperformance, and to support consumers
OL,19,Fwho receive compromised water services.
