OL,3,CWater firm pay outs: Who is eligible
OL,4,Cand how much compensation will be paid?
OL,6,FCurrently, some water companies
OL,7,Fvoluntarily offer compensation to
OL,8,Fcustomers who experience interruptions
OL,9,Fto their supply or other problems, but
OL,10,Fthere is no statutory requirement to
OL,11,Fdo so and rates can vary significantly
OL,12,Famong firms and location.
OL,14,FPayment rates for when water service
OL,15,Fstandards are not met have remained
OL,16,Funchanged since 2000, meaning reform
OL,17,Fis long overdue.
OL,19,FWho is eligible for compensation?
