OL,3,CWater firm pay outs: Who is eligible
OL,4,Cand how much compensation will be paid?
OL,6,FThe new rules will affect all water
OL,7,Fcompanies in the UK, with compensation
OL,8,Fbeing compulsory for failures
OL,9,Fincluding water supply outages, sewer
OL,10,Fflooding, and low water pressure.
OL,12,FCustomers who have problems like low
OL,13,Fwater pressure could receive payments
OL,14,Fof up to #250, compared to the #25
OL,15,Fcurrently available.
OL,17,FMeanwhile households affected by
OL,18,Fflooding inside their homes from
OL,19,Fsewers could receive #2,000 or more,
OL,20,Fcompared to #1,000 under current rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
