OL,3,CWater firm pay outs: Who is eligible
OL,4,Cand how much compensation will be paid?
OL,6,FThe changes will also see the list of
OL,7,Freasons for compensation expanded, to
OL,8,Finclude when boil notices are issued -
OL,9,Ffor example, when drinking water
OL,10,Fquality standards drop or when firms
OL,11,Ffail to conduct meter readings or
OL,12,Finstallations as promised.
OL,14,FHow much could I receive?
OL,16,FThe changes follow a public
OL,17,Fconsultation which found an average of
OL,18,F84% of water customers and 70% of
OL,19,Fbusinesses agreed with the proposals,
OL,20,Fthe Department for Environment, Food
OL,21,Fand Rural Affairs (Defra) said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
