OL,6,FA series of failures and outages in
OL,7,Frecent years means the public deserves
OL,8,Fbetter compensation and the sector
OL,9,Fneeds reform, according to Steve Reed,
OL,10,FSecretary of State for Environment,
OL,11,FFood, and Rural Affairs.
OL,13,F"Customers have too often been let
OL,14,Fdown by water companies, with supply
OL,15,Fcut off, low water pressure and in
OL,16,Fsome cases even contaminated tap
OL,17,Fwater," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
