OL,3,CWater firm pay outs: Who is eligible
OL,4,Cand how much compensation will be paid?
OL,6,FIn May, a 'Do Not Drink' notice was
OL,7,Fgiven to 600 properties in Bramley,
OL,8,FSussex, after a fuel leak. At the
OL,9,Ftime, Thames Water offered a voluntary
OL,10,F#30 payment. Under new rules, a
OL,11,Fcompulsory payment of #220 would have
OL,12,Fbeen given to households, and #440 to
OL,13,Fbusinesses.
OL,15,FNo compensation was given to residents
OL,16,Fin South Staffordshire last month
OL,17,Fwhose water supply was disrupted due
OL,18,Fto a burst water main. Under new
OL,19,Frules, households could have received
OL,20,Fa #150 payment, and businesses could
OL,21,Fhave been paid #300.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
