OL,6,FSimilarly, there was no entitlement
OL,7,Ffor compensation for the tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of people caught up in the
OL,9,Fcryptosporidium outbreak in Brixham,
OL,10,FDevon, earlier this year. Those
OL,11,Fcustomers could now receive at least
OL,12,F#10 per 24 hours, potentially
OL,13,Famounting to more than #500 for
OL,14,Fincidents over eight weeks.
OL,16,FHow do I apply for compensation, and
OL,17,Fwhen will the changes come into force?
OL,19,FThe changes are expected to come into
OL,20,Fforce next year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
