OL,3,CWater firm pay outs: Who is eligible
OL,4,Cand how much compensation will be paid?
OL,6,FAll compensation payments will be
OL,7,Fautomatic where water companies are
OL,8,Fable to identify that a customer is
OL,9,Feligible, Defra said.
OL,11,FCustomers will be able to apply for
OL,12,Fcompensation by contacting their
OL,13,Fcompany if they feel they are eligible
OL,14,Fand have not received a payment.
OL,15,FClaims should be made within three
OL,16,Fmonths of the incident.
OL,18,FThe changes form part of an overhaul
OL,19,Fby the government of how water
OL,20,Fcompanies are regulated and meet
OL,21,Fconsumer demand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
